<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{ city_name }} ZIP Drill v2 — Charter Opportunity by Zip Code</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      background: #f8f8f8;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #374151;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .meta {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .v2-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: #1e293b;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      padding: 1px 6px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      vertical-align: middle;
      margin-left: 6px;
    }
    .section { margin-bottom: 28px; }

    /* ── Map ── */
    .map-section {
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .map-section svg {
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 6px;
      background: #f9fafb;
    }

    /* ── Table ── */
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 6px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
    }

    thead th {
      background: #1e293b;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .05em;
      padding: 9px 10px;
      text-align: left;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    thead th.right  { text-align: right; }
    thead th.center { text-align: center; }

    tbody tr { border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    tbody tr:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    tbody tr:hover { background: #f0f9ff; }

    td {
      padding: 8px 10px;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
    td.right  { text-align: right; }
    td.center { text-align: center; }
    td.rank   { font-weight: 700; color: #64748b; width: 32px; }
    td.zip    { font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; width: 60px; }
    td.score  { font-weight: 700; font-size: 15px; color: #1e293b; width: 48px; }

    /* Score row tints — same as v1 */
    tr.score-high { background: #f0fdf4; }
    tr.score-mid  { background: #eff6ff; }
    tr.score-low  { background: #fefce8; }

    /* Dimension score chips */
    .dim-score {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
      padding: 2px 5px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      background: #f1f5f9;
      color: #334155;
      min-width: 28px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .dim-high { background: #dcfce7; color: #166534; }
    .dim-mid  { background: #dbeafe; color: #1e40af; }
    .dim-low  { background: #fef9c3; color: #854d0e; }

    /* Charter presence */
    .charter-zero  { font-weight: 600; color: #16a34a; }
    .charter-some  { font-weight: 600; color: #92400e; }
    .charter-names { font-size: 10px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 2px; }

    /* Transit cells */
    .transit-count {
      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .transit-na {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    /* Neighbor context cell */
    .nbr-context {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #374151;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .nbr-none {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .nbr-pill {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 10px;
      background: #f1f5f9;
      color: #475569;
      padding: 1px 5px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      margin-top: 3px;
      margin-right: 2px;
    }

    /* Insufficient data table */
    .insufficient-note {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #92400e;
      background: #fef3c7;
      border: 1px solid #fcd34d;
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .insufficient-table tbody tr { background: #f9fafb; }

    /* N/A badge */
    .na-badge {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      padding-top: 12px;
    }

    @media print {
      body { background: #fff; padding: 0; font-size: 11px; }
      table { box-shadow: none; }
      thead th { background: #1e293b !important;
                 -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; print-color-adjust: exact; }
      tr.score-high, tr.score-mid, tr.score-low {
        -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; print-color-adjust: exact; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <h1>{{ city_name }} — ZIP Drill Charter Opportunity <span class="v2-badge">v2</span></h1>
  <p class="meta">
    {{ zip_count }} zip codes · ranked by composite opportunity score · generated {{ generated_at }}
    · TIGER 2023 shapefiles · Transitland GTFS · Census ACS 2023 · topological neighbor analysis
  </p>

  {# ── SVG map ── #}
  <div class="map-section section">
    <h2>ZIP Code Map — Score by Tier</h2>
    {{ svg_map | safe }}
  </div>

  {# ── Main ranked table ── #}
  <div class="section">
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th class="center">Rank</th>
          <th>Zip</th>
          <th class="right">Score</th>
          <th class="center">Academic Need</th>
          <th>Charter Presence</th>
          <th class="right">School-Age Pop</th>
          <th class="right">Poverty Rate</th>
          <th class="right">ELL%</th>
          <th class="right">Transit Stops</th>
          <th class="right">Transit Routes</th>
          <th>Neighbor Context</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {% for s in ranked %}
          {# Row tier class #}
          {% if s.base.composite >= 7 %}
            {% set row_class = "score-high" %}
          {% elif s.base.composite >= 5 %}
            {% set row_class = "score-mid" %}
          {% else %}
            {% set row_class = "score-low" %}
          {% endif %}

          {# Academic need chip tier #}
          {% if s.base.academic_need >= 7 %}
            {% set an_class = "dim-high" %}
          {% elif s.base.academic_need >= 5 %}
            {% set an_class = "dim-mid" %}
          {% else %}
            {% set an_class = "dim-low" %}
          {% endif %}

        <tr class="{{ row_class }}">

          <td class="rank center">{{ s.base.rank }}</td>

          <td class="zip">{{ s.base.zip_code }}</td>

          <td class="score right">{{ "%.1f"|format(s.base.composite) }}</td>

          {# Academic need: chip + raw ELA% sublabel #}
          <td class="center">
            <span class="dim-score {{ an_class }}">{{ "%.1f"|format(s.base.academic_need) }}</span>
            {% if s.base.ela_proficiency_pct is not none %}
              <br><span style="font-size:10px;color:#6b7280;">
                {{ "%.0f"|format(s.base.ela_proficiency_pct) }}% ELA prof.
              </span>
            {% endif %}
          </td>

          {# Charter presence #}
          <td>
            {% if s.base.charter_count == 0 %}
              <span class="charter-zero">0 charters</span>
            {% else %}
              <span class="charter-some">{{ s.base.charter_count }}
                {{ "charter" if s.base.charter_count == 1 else "charters" }}</span>
              {% if s.base.charter_names %}
                <div class="charter-names">
                  {{ s.base.charter_names[:3] | join(", ") }}
                  {% if s.base.charter_names | length > 3 %}
                    +{{ s.base.charter_names | length - 3 }} more
                  {% endif %}
                </div>
              {% endif %}
            {% endif %}
            <div style="font-size:10px;color:#9ca3af;">{{ s.base.total_schools }} total schools</div>
          </td>

          {# School-age population #}
          <td class="right">
            {% if s.base.school_age_pop is not none %}
              {{ "{:,}".format(s.base.school_age_pop) }}
            {% else %}
              <span class="na-badge">N/A</span>
            {% endif %}
          </td>

          {# Poverty rate #}
          <td class="right">
            {% if s.base.poverty_rate_pct is not none %}
              {{ "%.1f"|format(s.base.poverty_rate_pct) }}%
            {% else %}
              <span class="na-badge">N/A</span>
            {% endif %}
          </td>

          {# ELL% #}
          <td class="right">
            {% if s.base.ell_pct_display is not none %}
              {{ "%.1f"|format(s.base.ell_pct_display) }}%
            {% else %}
              <span class="na-badge">N/A</span>
            {% endif %}
          </td>

          {# Transit stops (v2) #}
          <td class="right">
            {% if s.transit.transit_stop_count is not none %}
              <span class="transit-count">{{ s.transit.transit_stop_count }}</span>
            {% else %}
              <span class="transit-na">N/A</span>
            {% endif %}
          </td>

          {# Transit routes (v2) #}
          <td class="right">
            {% if s.transit.transit_route_count is not none %}
              <span class="transit-count">{{ s.transit.transit_route_count }}</span>
            {% else %}
              <span class="transit-na">N/A</span>
            {% endif %}
          </td>

          {# Neighbor context (v2) #}
          <td>
            {% set nc = s.neighbor_context %}
            {% if nc and nc.neighboring_zips %}
              <div class="nbr-context">
                {{ nc.neighboring_zips | length }} adj. ZIPs
                {%- if nc.avg_poverty_rate_pct is not none %}
                  · avg poverty {{ "%.0f"|format(nc.avg_poverty_rate_pct) }}%
                {%- endif %}
                · {{ nc.total_neighbor_charters }} charters nearby
              </div>
              <div style="margin-top:3px;">
                {% for z in nc.neighboring_zips %}
                  <span class="nbr-pill">{{ z }}</span>
                {% endfor %}
              </div>
            {% else %}
              <span class="nbr-none">no neighbors detected</span>
            {% endif %}
          </td>

        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  {# ── Insufficient data section ── #}
  {% if excluded %}
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Zip Codes — Insufficient Data</h2>
    <p class="insufficient-note">
      No Census population data returned. Likely non-residential (military, PO Box, industrial).
      Excluded from ranking.
    </p>
    <table class="insufficient-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Zip Code</th>
          <th>Total Schools</th>
          <th>Charter Count</th>
          <th class="right">Transit Stops</th>
          <th class="right">Transit Routes</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {% for s in excluded %}
        <tr>
          <td style="font-weight:600;">{{ s.base.zip_code }}</td>
          <td>{{ s.base.total_schools }}</td>
          <td>{{ s.base.charter_count }}</td>
          <td class="right">
            {% if s.transit.transit_stop_count is not none %}
              {{ s.transit.transit_stop_count }}
            {% else %}
              <span class="transit-na">N/A</span>
            {% endif %}
          </td>
          <td class="right">
            {% if s.transit.transit_route_count is not none %}
              {{ s.transit.transit_route_count }}
            {% else %}
              <span class="transit-na">N/A</span>
            {% endif %}
          </td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  <footer>
    ZIP Drill v2 — 5 dimensions, equal weights, uncalibrated. v2 addendum adds: TIGER/Line 2023
    ZCTA shapefiles (geographic context + SVG map), Transitland v2 GTFS transit stop/route counts
    (0.5-mile radius from ZCTA centroid), topological neighbor analysis (Census ACS 2023 demand
    signals for adjacent ZCTAs). Neighbor context is display-only and does not affect scores.
    Political, authorizer, and facilities signals not available at zip level.
    Proof of concept — do not use for real strategic decisions.
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
